OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1784751301
OL,3,C'Distraught' patient is unexpectedly
OL,4,Cbilled thousands
OL,6,FA patient at Guernsey's hospital says
OL,7,Fan unexpected bill for thousands of
OL,8,Fpounds has left him unable to afford
OL,9,Fto live.
OL,11,F68 year-old Robert Clancy received a
OL,12,Fbill for #4,500 from the Princess
OL,13,FElizabeth Hospital despite being told
OL,14,Fthere would be no charge for ongoing
OL,15,Fcare following a significant operation.
OL,17,FThe bill relates to charges for bed-
OL,18,Fblocking - relating to an extended
OL,19,Fstay he had at hospital following a
OL,20,Ffall and complications leading to a
OL,21,Ftoe amputation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1784751301
OL,3,C'Distraught' patient is unexpectedly
OL,4,Cbilled thousands
OL,6,FOnce Robert was deemed medically fit
OL,7,Fto go home, it took an additional
OL,8,Fthree and a half months to find a
OL,9,Fsuitable care home place where he
OL,10,Fcould access additional nursing care.
OL,12,FHe says a doctor, nursing staff, and
OL,13,Fadministrators at the PEH all assured
OL,14,Fhim he would not be charged for this
OL,15,Fprolonged stay.
OL,17,FRobert says the shock of the #4,500
OL,18,Fbill has been difficult for him to
OL,19,Fcope with.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1784751301
OL,3,C'Distraught' patient is unexpectedly
OL,4,Cbilled thousands
OL,6,F"I almost had another heart attack",
OL,7,Fhe told ITV News.
OL,9,F"I've had two, and that letter almost
OL,10,Fgave me another one - just the shock
OL,11,Fof it made me distraught. I suffer
OL,12,Ffrom depression anyway, and that made
OL,13,Fme even more depressed."
OL,15,FThe latest reminder, received on the
OL,16,F17th July, threatens further action
OL,17,Funless the bill is paid within the
OL,18,Fnext seven days - but Robert says he
OL,19,Fdoes not have the money, and is now
OL,20,Fworried about facing legal
OL,21,Framifications.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1784751301
OL,3,C'Distraught' patient is unexpectedly
OL,4,Cbilled thousands
OL,6,FHe explains that with all of his
OL,7,Fpension currently going towards
OL,8,Fnursing care, he is left with just #50
OL,9,Fper week to live on.
OL,11,FRobert adds the ordeal has placed a
OL,12,Fsignificant strain on his mental
OL,13,Fwellbeing.
OL,15,F"I'd rather be dead in my grave over
OL,16,Fthis, it's got that bad", he says.
OL,18,F"I'm giving up."
OL,20,FIn a statement, HSC's Director of Care
OL,21,FDelivery, Elaine Burgess, said:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1784751301
OL,3,C'Distraught' patient is unexpectedly
OL,4,Cbilled thousands
OL,6,F"If a person resident in a care home
OL,7,Fis admitted to hospital, and during
OL,8,Fthat time their condition
OL,9,Fdeteriorates, it is possible that a
OL,10,Fdecision will be made by a panel of
OL,11,Fnurses and social workers to discharge
OL,12,Fthem to a specialist nursing home,
OL,13,Frather than the care home they were
OL,14,Fpreviously resident in.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1784751301
OL,3,C'Distraught' patient is unexpectedly
OL,4,Cbilled thousands
OL,6,F"If that decision is taken, the person
OL,7,Fis welcome to stay in hospital without
OL,8,Fany cost for two weeks while they or
OL,9,Ftheir family secure a bed in a
OL,10,Fspecialist nursing home. After that
OL,11,Ftwo-week period, a charge will be
OL,12,Fapplied."
OL,14,FThe statement continues:
OL,16,F"We understand this could cause some
OL,17,Fadded stress to the person; however,
OL,18,Fit is critical that we free hospital
OL,19,Fbeds up to ensure they are available
OL,20,Ffor the health and care of all
OL,21,Fislanders.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1784751301
OL,3,C'Distraught' patient is unexpectedly
OL,4,Cbilled thousands
OL,6,F"We will take people's specific
OL,7,Fcircumstances into account before
OL,8,Fpursuing any payment. We'd urge anyone
OL,9,Fwith an outstanding payment to get in
OL,10,Ftouch if they cannot afford it.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1784751301
OL,3,C'Distraught' patient is unexpectedly
OL,4,Cbilled thousands
OL,6,F"We are genuinely sorry if anyone was
OL,7,Fmisinformed, and we will use this
OL,8,Fopportunity to review how we
OL,9,Fcommunicate these matters to ensure it
OL,10,Fis being made clear to all in future.
OL,11,FIt is important to note, however, this
OL,12,Fis not a new policy. It also remains
OL,13,Fthe case that A&E charges apply,
OL,14,Fhowever secondary treatment (non-
OL,15,Fprivate) within the hospital does not
OL,16,Fhave a cost attached."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
